{"tid":1475464,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【連登仔齊撳錢】港元拆息大幅抽升，隔夜急飆至1.2厘","createTime":"2019-08-15T13:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T14:55:09.000Z","uid":66271,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b9a892083075f89dd8bfd97fab055dab79a935e2","tid":1475464,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2018/6/1527796044_Al-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2018%2F6%2F1527796044_Al-1280w.jpg&h=610a4f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港元拆息大幅抽升，隔夜急飆至1.2厘，1星期及2星期拆息分別升至逾1.7厘及1.8厘。以往拆息一般在臨近月結及大型新股招股期間飆升，在兩項因素缺席下，仍抽升並不常見，不排與本地政治因素有關。港滙走軟，今早低見7.8462，最近報7.8391。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港銀行公會數據，短息升幅較急，隔夜拆息升至1.2厘，較上交易日上升0.78厘；1星期及2星期拆息最新報1.71857 厘及1.88228 厘，較上交易日上升0.77厘及0.49厘。<br />\n<br />\n1個月期拆息抽升至2.14286 厘，較上日升0.3厘。3個月及6個月拆息最新報2.35厘及2.36054 厘；12個月拆息報2.4325厘。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐亞太區副主席兼行政總裁王冬勝接受《星島日報》訪問時被問及香港有否因應近期事件而出現資金流走，他指暫不見有明顯的資金外流，但見有少量流走情況。<br />\n<br />\n對於本港近期發生的示威衝突事件愈見暴力，王冬勝認為，全體市民必須向暴力說不，因暴力事件既危害公眾安全，嚴重影響香港國際的形象，香港國際金融中心的地位和聲譽得來不易，港人應加以珍惜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627ef911a29b507702d5ee4b2c06d83797bb0e23","tid":1475464,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15497d2f273d74446f6cbfbf927c716041748960","tid":1475464,"uid":57424,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:21:00.000Z","msg":"鏈鐙釨好撚有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求包養(眼屎仲係處)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfed49582e56d784b22329ee8bc85683d3e7a9e","tid":1475464,"uid":59955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9f4062ba2ab6b094f1382b18d26bcf4c46d6d2","tid":1475464,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:21:32.000Z","msg":"向暴警說不"},{"pid":"579ce897313ba55703c19c02cfe19f7b09ada671","tid":1475464,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3dd400424b0d981d57f4fde2fc119b9db23a07f","tid":1475464,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3424fb15256ffb3b569f232f6c6d17ad6a2d1c55","tid":1475464,"uid":198008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"會唔會港元甩勾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7377714229150a24a648c4da39b384951cfcaee6","tid":1475464,"uid":101945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:53:31.000Z","msg":"升到3% 先講啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔冇錢的<br />\n<br />\n#燈燈燈燈"},{"pid":"e7dfe6d7160fbabd31e4f97f6b12f11b53c1516a","tid":1475464,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:54:10.000Z","msg":"No stake in the society"},{"pid":"1cbfeeb16c3770cac83b5293d4094dac0116f1d7","tid":1475464,"uid":253016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:57:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家就係和理非同